  "texts": [
    "2024) and (Wei et al. 2024) is the first work leveraging PEFT to fine-tuning VFMs for Domain Generalization (DG) (Bi et al.",
    "In the RS field, the exploration of PEFT is also vigorous.",
    "For example, UPetu (Dong, Gu, and Liu 2024) addresses storage for dense prediction tasks.",
    "TEA (Hu et al. 2024) uses an adapter network and top-down guidance for detection and segmentation tasks.",
    "(Pu and Xu 2025) also leverage LoRA to solve oriented detection task."
  ]
